# exam-papers

Go CLI/API for fetching Irish State Exam papers from examinations.ie.

- Build: `go build -o exam-papers ./cmd/exam-papers/`
- Unit tests: `go test ./pkg/examapi/ -run 'Test[^I]'`
- Integration tests: `EXAM_INTEGRATION=1 go test ./pkg/examapi/ -run TestIntegration`
- The site obfuscates URLs with shifted ASCII codes. See `encodeParam`/`decodeParam` in `pkg/examapi/client.go`.
- The server generates random offsets per page load, so action values must be parsed from each HTML response (see `parseActions`).
- Rate limiting: Cloudflare enforced. Client uses 500ms delays + exponential backoff on 403/429.
- Subject codes: 1=Irish, 2=English, 3=Maths, 21=Physics, 22=Chemistry, 25=Biology
